  description: Increases Armor by 5 and grants 15 Starting Mana. Upon casting an
    ability, the wearer gains a magical shield equal to 50% of their Maximum Mana
    for 5 seconds. A blessed kite shield emblazoned with the radiant sun of Pelor;
    it converts the wearer's spiritual conviction into a shimmering wall of light
    that deflects even the most thunderous blows.
